name: fnf vs the white imposter (joke mod)
name_original: fnf vs the white imposter (joke mod)
description:
Default key binds are DFJK, you can change this in options along with note colors and you can even turn off screen effects if you easily have seizures. oh and theres downscroll.

other than that,  yeah just another joke mod featuring a among us guy with no sprite sheet, just a idle.

and if you want to play it again you have to refresh the page.
